{"tid":1170911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"威猛公馬秀80CM求愛！女帝馬狠踹一記「芳香腳」　下秒牠倒地石化了","createTime":"2019-05-25T10:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T15:09:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"65e9fd7540cc839b7312f10f0a09e0bb399eb78f","tid":1170911,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"電影圈最近吹起女力當道的旋風，沒想到連動物也相繼跟上。巴西有間馬場的公馬疑似正處於發情期，一看到隔壁的母馬便展露自己雄壯的「80CM」想要求愛。在工作人員的安排之下，決定讓2馬在同一個圍欄裡相處看看，誰知道母馬直接用後腿朝著公馬的頭部狠踹，一腳立刻讓對方倒地不起。<br />\n <br />\n影片一開始，毛色油亮黝黑的公馬在圍欄裡，情緒似乎有些浮躁，四肢不停地小踱步，看到隔壁棚的「美女」，生殖器的部位也充血了起來。一旁的馴馬師見狀後，趕緊把馬兒給拉開，但雄壯的公馬又隨即抗拒，說什麼就是想要近距離和母馬接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NhdOS04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhdOS04.png&h=e5800dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過程中可以看到，母馬一看到公馬反應非常淡定，但在馴馬師的牽引之下，牠還是被迫進了跟公馬一樣的圍欄。雙方見到面後，情緒高亢的公馬一直在原地發出嘶嘶聲，反觀母馬似乎有些緊張，在原地轉圈，並且在轉第二圈的同時，後腿順勢一抬，朝著公馬的頭部狠踹一腳，直接讓對方倒地。<br />\n <br />\n馴馬師見雙方約會破局後，趕緊先將氣噗噗的母馬拉到一旁去安撫，讓牠情緒稍微穩定點。而公馬的情況相當不樂觀，一開始是倒在地上雙腳抽搐、大小便失禁，但過沒幾秒，便一動也不動了；只見當鏡頭拉近時，牠嘴巴微張、雙眼無神，而且身體也彷彿沒有了呼吸，現場人員初步判斷馬兒已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQYOS1n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQYOS1n.png&h=6c1cbf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這段影片最近被網友分享到臉書公開社團，目前已累積85萬次的觀看次數，許多人看完都留言說，「這腳堪比女帝的芳香腳」、「爆頭了....」、「年輕人還是太衝動了」、「踹一腳屎都噴出來了」、「直接跳過交配，投胎去了」、「傳說中的天殘腳！？」、「這死的還真冤」、「沒有情投意合應是送作堆，當然不高興阿」。<br />\n <br />\n不過也有不少網友推測公馬的死因，「應該是舌頭咬到了」、「被踢到腦門，一蹄斃命」、「踢中腦門掛了，都翻白眼了」、「那匹馬很可憐，應該是瞬間顱內增壓導致內出血，看到牠大便失禁說明已經沒救了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TDU2Xtj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTDU2Xtj.png&h=f9c934aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/miao.hui.56/videos/1533986913404824/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmiao.hui.56%2Fvideos%2F1533986913404824%2F&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62I5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=af950033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/miao.hui.56/videos/1533986913404824/</a>"},{"pid":"0fd5f6d3e316de4ca82f5c15bdfa32a2caf5ae10","tid":1170911,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"以為踢到下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0074953c023e334a2c46f15a1c5e6737c7cfcf","tid":1170911,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d19457cbe6109e6f6f0c2cce522fb61918a81ce2","tid":1170911,"uid":137627,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"屌老味拍果位係咪低鳩能<br />\n無個畫面睇得晒隻馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3831741cc01be7e187a2c4a43987f96888b3ff1e","tid":1170911,"uid":205619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:34:15.000Z","msg":"死得好冤枉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29578725be935ed791a1ea25f89608d9f965f392","tid":1170911,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ec3056845999ca8070b1fded99fa1815e15cec","tid":1170911,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a0074953c023e334a2c46f15a1c5e6737c7cfcf","tid":1170911,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"連馬女都證明:女人係比較喜歡洋腸"},{"pid":"fccac5511bbd5ff39d0e2f6e85937846bf9a337a","tid":1170911,"uid":13303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢中文黎生殖器的部位"},{"pid":"0858307ef072e2ab6242c90ae34cfad576d7a26a","tid":1170911,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"快狠準"},{"pid":"a6f781ee33df9ab07246a9608c82d06d2e4a036c","tid":1170911,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"劉馬車嘅下場"},{"pid":"48834463fa64cc1472eaa45f182d43ef64c51c7d","tid":1170911,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"另精馬上風"},{"pid":"98f971c3630fc5627019600e0557821c43e8278b","tid":1170911,"uid":88366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"一訓底即刻瀨屎<br />\n死得咁快"},{"pid":"b3d8f9dc6e6344ff65400450b9220ee666d400e4","tid":1170911,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"到死都仲係青頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea53345a329848f216e863d0677e8b830e33b43","tid":1170911,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"四腳動物淨係得後入一招"},{"pid":"132818a896dfd847fc2cfaa639f9fde39d3f6bbf","tid":1170911,"uid":60303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"862de16129873e25879f5022440fe0a051863dd2","tid":1170911,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"學子華話齋, 最慘係埋唔到舟"},{"pid":"e6a2f70aa3f2753743b9aaef3505a61fec5cf485","tid":1170911,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478aad40d65c43df1b6a29e421102d2ec0082845","tid":1170911,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"色字頭上一把刀,原來動物都啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}